---
description: Security guidance
globs:
    - "SECURITY.md"
    - "docs/SECURITY.md"
    - ".github/workflows/**/*"
    - "src/app/api/**/*"
    - "contracts/src/**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

Treat wallets, bearer secrets, private keys, RPC credentials, email tokens, and
deployment credentials as sensitive. Model trust boundaries explicitly, document
new risks, and update `SECURITY.md` for auth, authorization, encryption, oracle,
dependency, or incident-response changes.
